# SHA256 checksums for binary fidelity reference firmware.
# Each entry corresponds to a pre-built ELF validated on real silicon.
# DO NOT update a checksum without re-validating the binary on real hardware first.
# Format: <sha256>  <path-relative-to-tests/firmware/>
#
# To add a new binary:
#   sha256sum path/to/firmware.elf >> tests/firmware/SHA256SUMS
#   # then validate on silicon, capture golden_uart.txt, commit both together
